# Agentrade Engine v2 — Environment Variables

## Hyperliquid credentials
HL_PRIVATE_KEY=0x_your_private_key_here
HL_WALLET_ADDRESS=0x_your_wallet_address_here
HL_TESTNET=true

## Telegram Bot
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here
TELEGRAM_ADMIN_CHAT_ID=0
